This project had 4 people working on. My assignment was to do  1.1A, 1.1B and 1.10, which featured creating a bisection algorithm and a Newtons Method Algorithm
There will be a text based file to see the code easily and the downloadable maple Code to run

This is a a Maple implementation of the Bisection Method for numerical root-finding. 
The program estimates the required iteration count, approximates roots of nonlinear functions to a specified tolerance,
and displays each iteration to illustrate the convergence of the algorithm.
